Remember that time President Donald Trump got seriously freaked out by a bald eagle? Trevor Noah does. And on Monday's broadcast of "The Daily Show," the host used the incident to explain why Trump would never, ever actually run in to confront a school shooter (despite his claims to the contrary). "Really? That guy? That guy was gonna run in and stop a school shooter?" asked Noah. "Get the fuck out of here, man." Check out the full segment above.